question: Can provide me with demographic analysis of all people seen by Custody Healthcare between 1stÂ January 2024 to today
sql:
SELECT 
    G.[Name],
    COUNT(R.id) AS NumberOfReferrals,
    ROUND(COUNT(R.id) * 100.0 / SUM(COUNT(r.id)) OVER(), 2) AS PercentageOfTotal
FROM Referrals R
Join DetainedPersons DP on DP.id = R.detainedpersonId
Join Maintenance_GenderType G on G.Id = DP.Maintenance_GenderTypeId
WHERE CAST(r.ReferralCreatedDateTime AS DATE) BETWEEN '2024-01-01' and CAST(GETDATE() AS DATE)
GROUP BY DP.Maintenance_GenderTypeId, G.[Name]
ORDER BY NumberOfReferrals DESC;

    ROUND(COUNT(R.id) * 100.0 / SUM(COUNT(r.id)) OVER(), 2) AS PercentageOfTotal
FROM Referrals R
Join DetainedPersons DP on DP.id = R.detainedpersonId
Join Maintenance_GenderType G on G.Id = DP.Maintenance_GenderTypeId
WHERE CAST(r.ReferralCreatedDateTime AS DATE) BETWEEN '2024-01-01' and CAST(GETDATE() AS DATE)
GROUP BY DP.Maintenance_GenderTypeId, G.[Name]
ORDER BY NumberOfReferrals DESC;
